briefdescription.para: Adds an interval to a datetime.
Returns the interval between two datetimes.

parameterdescription.para: datetime to subtract, ie subtract datetime2 from datetime1

briefdescription.para: Returns the interval between two dates.

parameterdescription.para: date to subtract, ie subtract date2 from date1

briefdescription.para: Returns the interval between two times.

parameterdescription.para: time to subtract, ie subtract time2 from time1
